{"tid":973534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(波蘭調查) 男性為事業出賣肉體, 比女性更可能獲晉升","createTime":"2019-01-08T08:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T09:57:53.000Z","uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"116f6b39ed38244eb7f29ff93da6d6d1fd65afdb","tid":973534,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T08:47:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2225793\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2225793&d=4Ag1gy5rOgZ5EjT6Eq90HNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b295e264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2225793</a><br />\n<br />\n職場調查指近 3 成人曾跟上司上床！近 15％ 可升職加薪<br />\n | Siu Yeung | 07-12-2018 20:09 | <br />\n<br />\n看劇集不時都有上司跟下屬發生性關係的橋段，在現實世界裏這情況究竟是否常見？早前波蘭職場網站 Zety 進行了調查，發現有近 3 成的女性及男生員工曾與上司發生性行為，當有中有人因此升職加薪，也有人要離職，甚至被敲詐。<br />\n<br />\n該項調查找來 1000 多名受訪者，<strong>當中有約 27% 女性和 28% 男性承認曾與上司發生性行為，近 40% 人更表示不止一次。值得意的是男性下屬與上司發生性關係的比例比女性多，其中一個原因可能是男性比女性更易獲得晉升機會。</strong>至於跟上司發生性行為的原因，其中 21.8% 的受訪者表示為了獲得權力。<br />\n<br />\n在曾與上司發生性行為的受訪者中，有 25.5% 人跟上司建立了親密的伴侶關係，並有近 15% 的人獲加薪，13%的人獲升職。不過也有 10.6% 人表示公司開始有流言、14% 找另一份工作、3.4% 的人更被降職。<br />\n<br />\n另外 58% 受訪者表示，在職場上有認識的同事曾跟上司發生性行為，當中有超過 6 成人表示自己不會作出任何特別舉動，但有 16% 人表示會與同事分享消息；更分別有 4.2% 和 3.2%人表示會利用這機會敲詐上級和相關同事。"},{"pid":"8439cf8e0e2f5712d06007914aaa9246b62eb55a","tid":973534,"uid":179356,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"男下屬同男上司"},{"pid":"e5f8be5ba4499c11bf96c6a8690c6a6f9853b9c3","tid":973534,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T08:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ee97289376c585ce5b492289e181e3a94a1e26","tid":973534,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:02:58.000Z","msg":"波蘭仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1348298a5eff520b45ca95807ac7d8806a51daa9","tid":973534,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:04:55.000Z","msg":"hehe味濃"},{"pid":"87c565324bf79a88cca15f07dbbbea0327328261","tid":973534,"uid":225295,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d0ee97289376c585ce5b492289e181e3a94a1e26","tid":973534,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:02:58.000Z","msg":"波蘭仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i-h2.pinimg.com/564x/0e/94/66/0e9466dc557cb1e2e33a6c8f4a25f6b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi-h2.pinimg.com%2F564x%2F0e%2F94%2F66%2F0e9466dc557cb1e2e33a6c8f4a25f6b8.jpg&h=32980ab8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b398279f72578dfa3c4c3588ce4e97adf0bf30c4","tid":973534,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"87c565324bf79a88cca15f07dbbbea0327328261","tid":973534,"uid":225295,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d0ee97289376c585ce5b492289e181e3a94a1e26","tid":973534,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:02:58.000Z","msg":"波蘭仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i-h2.pinimg.com/564x/0e/94/66/0e9466dc557cb1e2e33a6c8f4a25f6b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi-h2.pinimg.com%2F564x%2F0e%2F94%2F66%2F0e9466dc557cb1e2e33a6c8f4a25f6b8.jpg&h=32980ab8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:11:30.000Z","msg":"咁冇得比，只可以講句來生要做波蘭仔"},{"pid":"35dafbd568668068502c9b3ed9af131bc6cf5f91","tid":973534,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:47:39.000Z","msg":"男人出賣屎忽個心理關口<br />\n同女人出賣個閪差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510ae4e8f9c736e9e3fe3acc462abc9432720263","tid":973534,"uid":131884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"我老細幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔為權力，只為上床"}]}